These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, musical
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | zombie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, swimming
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Sport         | swimming   | tennis      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

 #################################

 
